Constant Field Values

FAIL

public static final int FAIL
A response tag to indicate that something is seriously wrong with the corresponding call and/or the prover and a failure has taken place. A response code of FAIL typically indicates a non-correctable situation. The getInfo() method should be consulted for additional information, and no further calls, but for SortedProver.stopProver() should be made.
